al immune\nresponse while dampening inflammatory signaling. In addition, metabolic\ngenes have experienced repeated expansions related to convergent shifts\nto plant-based diets. Our analyses support the hypothesis that, in\ntandem with flight, ancestral bats had evolved a unique set of immune\nadaptations whose functional implications remain to be explored.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Santillan, Diana Moreno", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Lama, Tanya", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Guerrero, Yocelyn Guti\u00e9rrez", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Brown, Alexis", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Donat, Paul", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Zhao, Huabin", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Rossiter, Stephen", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Yohe, Laurel", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Potter, Joshua", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Teeling, Emma", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Vernes, Sonja", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Davies, Kalina", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Myers, Eugene", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hughes, Graham", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Huang, Zixia", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Hoffmann, Federico G.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Corthals, Angelique", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Ray, David", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Davalos, Liliana", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/81da613ed065b82681089cae91a9e988", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/98f8d2fe20b972f60ec38270ae2848092e8dc647c27b4563841f1af87e26434f", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/9TABXIU4", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/9TABXIU4", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://m